   <concept id="FAR_52_214_18" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">52.214-18</ph> Preparation of Bids-Construction.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="provision" class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p " id="d3186e8">As prescribed in <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="14.201-6.dita#FAR_14_201_6"
                     base="i1110459"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">14.201-6</xref>(l)</ph>, insert the following provision:</p>
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps" id="d3186e15">Preparation of Bids-Construction <ph outputclass="SmCaps" class="- topic/ph ">(Apr 1984)</ph>
         </p>
         <ol id="d3151e25" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3186e21">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            Bids must be-</p>
               <ol id="d3151e35" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d3186e27">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                Submitted on the forms furnished by the Government or on copies of those forms, and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d3186e32">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Manually signed.</i> The person signing a bid must initial each erasure or change appearing on any bid form.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3186e39">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            The bid form may require bidders to submit bid prices for one or more items on various bases, including-</p>
               <ol id="d3151e68" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d3186e45">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                Lump sum bidding;</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d3186e50">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                Alternate prices;</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d3186e55">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
								                Units of construction; or</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d3186e60">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
								                Any combination of paragraphs (b)(1) through (b)(3) of this provision.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3186e65">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
						            If the solicitation requires bidding on all items, failure to do so will disqualify the bid. If bidding on all items is not required, bidders should insert the words "no bid" in the space provided for any item on which no price is submitted.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3186e70">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
						            Alternate bids will not be considered unless this solicitation authorizes their submission.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="Endofprovision">(End of provision)</p>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
